    {
      "headings": [
        {
          "tag": "h2",
          "text": "Why You Need to Automate ITAM Now"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Cut Equipment Provisioning Time"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Productivity Gained Every Day"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Lower Cost-per-Asset-Loss"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Real-Time  Visibility"
        }
      ],
      "paragraphs": [
        "Organizations that embrace AI today see faster growth, smarter decisions, and stronger internal service connections.",
        "Provision a new hire's full equipment load (laptop, monitor, etc.) instantly via a single chat command, eliminating manual UI navigation.\n\nRequest a call",
        "IT and HR teams reclaim valuable time each day by replacing spreadsheet-era workflows with simple, plain-language conversational commands.\n\nREQUEST A CALL",
        "Real-time visibility and accountability mitigate the high costs associated with lost, misallocated, or underutilized company equipment.\n\nREQUEST A CALL",
        "Instantly retrieve all user and asset records from Snipe-IT, providing an objective, real-time view of inventory and allocation status.\n\nREQUEST A CALL"
      ],
      "listItems": [],
      "ctas": [],
      "images": []
    },
